request.description:
# Set Policy Fragments

Set multiple policy fragments together. The fragments may or may not exist at the destination. Each fragment is either created if it doesn't exist at target or updated if it already exists.

Input: same structure as createPolicyFragment but as an array instead of a single web api service

``` json
{
  "input": [
    {
      "name" : "New policy somewhere",
      "folderPath" : "/migrationTest",
      "policy" : {
      "xml" : "wsp:Policy...>"
      }
    }
  ]
}

```

